<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Nous espérons que ce guide a été utile pour ceux qui souhaitent en savoir plus sur la culture du travail et les relations professionnelles en Turquie. Pour toute question ou pour plus d&#8217;informations, n&#8217;hésitez pas à visiter le site web de RoadToStudy !</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2026-04-20T04:00:00Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-14T15:47:21Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/scientific-event-and-organization-support-in-turkey.webp","alt":"Scientific event and organization supports in Turkey","title":"scientific-event-and-organization-support-in-turkey"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'fr' AND "slug" = 'culture-du-travail-et-relations-professionnelles-en-turquie' );
