<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Discussion and debate skills in Turkish are crucial for individuals to express their thoughts effectively and to develop their ability to understand opposing views. These skills contribute significantly not only to academic success but also to social relationships and professional life. For international students, developing these skills will enrich their educational experience in Turkey. If you want to improve your discussion and debate skills, you can start by applying the strategies shared in this article.</p>
