<p>Language (TOEFL, IELTS, YDS), IT (AWS, Cisco), project management (PMP), and MYK certificates are the most valued.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2026-06-09T11:00:00Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-16T19:53:05Z') WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'certificates-and-career-opportunities-in-turkey' );
