<li><strong>Work Permit Application:</strong> With the qualification certificate, you must apply to the Ministry of Labour and Social Security.</li>
<li><strong>Awaiting the Result:</strong> Wait for the application to be evaluated and the work permit to be approved.</li>
</ul>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Practical Example</h3>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If an international student wants to work in the field of engineering, they must first obtain a professional qualification certificate and then apply for a work permit.</p>
<h2 id="denklik-surecinde-dikkat-edilmesi-gerekenler" class="wp-block-heading">Important Points to Consider During the Recognition Process</h2>
