<div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]">
<div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words dark markdown-new-styling">
<h3 data-start="0" data-end="32">What are the average salaries in Turkey?</h3>
<p data-start="34" data-end="336" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">In Turkey, male wage earners receive an average gross monthly salary of <strong>24,011 TL</strong>, while women receive <strong>23,344 TL</strong>. The average gross earning per person was <strong>26,402 TL</strong>. The average gross monthly earning for male wage earners is <strong>26,638 TL</strong>, and for women, it is <strong>25,931 TL</strong>.</p>
<h3 data-start="121" data-end="162">Which professions earn the highest salaries?</h3>
<p data-start="163" data-end="271">The highest salaries are earned by <strong>bank managers, engineers, doctors, and senior technology specialists</strong>.</p>
<article class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" dir="auto" tabindex="-1" data-turn-id="request-WEB:b4d53112-d8dd-402a-8555-40c6278ee8fa-13" data-testid="conversation-turn-28" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant">
