<div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]">
<div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words dark markdown-new-styling">
<h3 data-start="413" data-end="449">Professions that earn 100,000 TL</h3>
<p data-start="450" data-end="585" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">In Turkey, <strong>CEOs, senior executives, some private sector doctors, and senior engineers</strong> can earn 100,000 TL or more per month.</p>
